title: GORGEOUS CORNER UNIT IN BISCAYNE BEACH!!
posting_body: ["Come live in the most exclusive building's in Edgewater.", 'Amazing location with expansive views to the east, south and west that provide sunrise and sunset views of Miami Skyline.', 'Enjoy a fully furnished 2,298 square feet of luxurious features throughout the generously sized 3 bedrooms + Den and 4 bathrooms.', 'Ocean-framed Master bedroom, living room and dining room with open kitchen.', 'Oversized balcony with unbelievable views.', '10 ft ceilings, floor to ceiling impact windows, open kitchen, Utility room with washer + dryer.', 'Biscayne Beach offers 5-star concierge services, meeting rooms, 2 pools, beach club, 2 tennis courts, 1 basketball court, massage rooms, beauty salon, spa, dog park, resort style amenities, and world top-level security.', 'First and last month, plus security.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
